Roach Tells CNBC That U.S. on ‘Brink’ of Relapse Into Recession

-- B y   S c o t t   H a m i l t o n
-- 
2011-09-22T11:06:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/roach-tells-cnbc-that-u-s-on-brink-of-relapse-into-recession.html
Stephen Roach , non-executive
chairman of Morgan Stanley  Asia , said the  U.S. economy  is on the
“brink” of a relapse into a recession and is facing a
Japanese-style stagnation scenario.  Roach made the comments in an interview on CNBC today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
